  <p>μμ </p>
</blockquote>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>shared_ptr&lt;int&gt; ptr01(new int(5)); // intν• shared_ptrμΈ ptr01μ„ μ„ μ–Έν•κ³  μ΄κΈ°ν™”ν•¨.

